Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:56.59,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:06.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
